00:26:33.280 --> 00:26:36.881
So Ali was using all these kinds of mind tricks

609
00:26:36.883 --> 00:26:41.018
but other elite athletes now routinely use a thing

610
00:26:41.020 --> 00:26:42.553
called “mental rehearsal”

611
00:26:42.555 --> 00:26:46.223
to focus and prepare themselves, and also

612
00:26:46.225 --> 00:26:50.728
rehearse every move, because they all understand

613
00:26:50.730 --> 00:26:54.098
that the mind can’t really distinguish between

614
00:26:54.100 --> 00:26:55.900
a thought and an action.

615
00:26:55.901 --> 00:27:00.571
And that the body believes that it is

616
00:27:00.573 --> 00:27:02.373
going through the action when it just

617
00:27:02.375 --> 00:27:03.875
mentally rehearses it.

618
00:27:03.876 --> 00:27:06.343
And it makes those same neural connections

619
00:27:06.345 --> 00:27:09.646
to the muscles, so in a sense paves the way

620
00:27:09.648 --> 00:27:11.550
for the action to follow.

621
00:27:11.551 --> 00:27:14.051
<v Regina>Let’s talk about in the spiritual realms</v>

