00:27:14.053 --> 00:27:17.755
of mastery, and moving into the subject

623
00:27:17.756 --> 00:27:19.756
of coherence.

624
00:27:19.758 --> 00:27:22.526
<v ->Most of the intention masters that I spoke with</v>

