00:27:32.238 --> 00:27:36.006
and it didn’t seem to matter which technique they used,

629
00:27:36.008 --> 00:27:39.410
whether it was using meditation with a mantra,

630
00:27:39.411 --> 00:27:44.181
or a tone, or drums, or sounds, of their breath,

631
00:27:44.183 --> 00:27:46.618
or their rosary beads.

632
00:27:46.620 --> 00:27:49.286
It all seemed to work, it all focused the mind

633
00:27:49.288 --> 00:27:52.056
away from the chatter of the every day

634
00:27:52.058 --> 00:27:55.593
to a deeper level, and once they were there

635
00:27:55.595 --> 00:27:59.630
they would work hard on uncoupling from the ego.

636
00:27:59.631 --> 00:28:04.068
They moved aside into a more, as some of them described,

637
00:28:04.070 --> 00:28:07.138
“impersonal space,” where they had basically

638
00:28:07.140 --> 00:28:08.640
made contact with the field.

639
00:28:08.641 --> 00:28:10.841
So that’s a really important thing too,

640
00:28:10.843 --> 00:28:13.076
is working on techniques that will

641
00:28:13.078 --> 00:28:16.648
shed the ego so that you are

642
00:28:16.650 --> 00:28:18.983
in a sense one with the field,

643
00:28:18.985 --> 00:28:22.186
and you have removed this sense of separation

644
00:28:22.188 --> 00:28:24.956
with which we usually live our lives.

645
00:28:24.958 --> 00:28:28.493
They all talked about using compassion,

646
00:28:28.495 --> 00:28:30.761
sending out their intention from the heart.

647
00:28:30.763 --> 00:28:33.665
It seemed to work best with intention masters

648
00:28:33.666 --> 00:28:38.666
if the subject of their intention had similar beliefs.

649
00:28:40.440 --> 00:28:42.206
It also seemed to work best

650
00:28:42.208 --> 00:28:46.010
when the intention master was feeling well in himself.

