1031
00:45:17.803 --> 00:45:21.038
focus on what is; what’s going on at that moment.

1032
00:45:21.040 --> 00:45:23.940
And so that kind of intense mind-state,

1033
00:45:23.941 --> 00:45:27.110
which is hard for us to do without practice,

1034
00:45:27.111 --> 00:45:30.613
is very helpful in becoming a master intender,

1035
00:45:30.615 --> 00:45:33.150
because what you want to do is ultimately

1036
00:45:33.151 --> 00:45:36.220
keep into that focused state, and then

1037
00:45:36.221 --> 00:45:38.488
send your intention.

1038
00:45:38.490 --> 00:45:40.423
Other techniques are important.

