00:45:40.425 --> 00:45:43.026
Other techniques that are important include

1040
00:45:43.028 --> 00:45:45.628
choosing your intention space.

1041
00:45:45.630 --> 00:45:47.965
I suggest this because there’s a lot of

1042
00:45:47.966 --> 00:45:51.635
laboratory evidence showing that when they do

1043
00:45:51.636 --> 00:45:54.238
mind-over-matter experiments in the lab,

