00:45:54.240 --> 00:45:57.073
it works faster and better

1045
00:45:57.075 --> 00:45:59.610
as time goes on if they can carry out

1046
00:45:59.611 --> 00:46:03.046
those experiments in the same place over time.

1047
00:46:03.048 --> 00:46:05.081
So that suggests to me

1048
00:46:05.083 --> 00:46:08.151
that in a sense you create a sacred space

1049
00:46:08.153 --> 00:46:10.955
when you send intention in a space.

1050
00:46:10.956 --> 00:46:14.558
So it means just cleaning up and clearing up

1051
00:46:14.560 --> 00:46:17.193
one little place in your house,

1052
00:46:17.195 --> 00:46:19.028
or in your office or whatever,

1053
00:46:19.030 --> 00:46:20.931
that becomes your space.

1054
00:46:20.933 --> 00:46:24.901
And always sending intention from that space.

1055
00:46:24.903 --> 00:46:27.336
Now suppose you’re traveling.

1056
00:46:27.338 --> 00:46:30.273
You can still mentally travel to your space

1057
00:46:30.275 --> 00:46:32.141
and then send an intention there.

1058
00:46:32.143 --> 00:46:33.045
<v Regina>That’s a very good point, yes.</v>

