00:47:08.280 --> 00:47:09.746
So I think it’s important—

1074
00:47:09.748 --> 00:47:11.015
<v Regina>Not efficient.</v>

1075
00:47:11.016 --> 00:47:12.581
<v ->Yeah, no, exactly.</v>

